title: 2016 Preseason Power Poll
itunes:title: 2016 Preseason Power Poll
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Colleen Wolfe – discuss the latest NFL news including Teddy Bridgewater’s statement after his gruesome injury and the newest wrinkle in the Colin Kaepernick situation. Then, the heroes dive into their annual Preseason Power Poll and break down where teams rank and which teams have the best chance to make it to Super Bowl LI.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
